  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a post-marketing surveillance study in Japan that will evaluate the safety and
      patient satisfaction with GLASH VISTA™ (bimatoprost cutaneous solution 0.03%) in the
      treatment of hypotrichosis of the eyelashes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
